Change Log for Text::Smart
==========================

v1.0.2: (23-02-2008)
--------------------

 * Added example programs
 * Added META.yml
 * Added warnings pragma to all modules
 * Added simple command line tool for processing data

v1.0.1: (20-08-2006)
--------------------

 * Completed POD documentation
 * Added POD coverage testing
 * Added functional testing
 * Ability to escape input text

v1.0.0: (12-05-2004)
--------------------

 * Initial release.

